data.description: Triplex with plenty of off street parking and all 3 units having 5 unrelated rental licensure now available. Unit 1 (main level unit) has expansive living room in front and eat-in kitchen to the back. Two bedrooms, a study room and a full size bathroom finish off the floor. This unit has been under renovation and project will not be completed by current owner. This unit is currently vacant but has been rented in the past for $950. Washer/dryer hook-up in kitchen for this unit. Access is thru the side door. Unit 2 (Upstairs) has been renovated with new flooring, new appliances, fresh paint, new countertops and new water heater. It has four bedrooms and one bathroom and was rented for $1500. No laundry access for this unit. Access is thru the side door. Unit 3 (lower level) has 4 bedrooms and one full bathroom. Washer and dryer in utility room solely used by this unit. Access is thru the back door by the parking area. Tenants pay electrical, owner pays city and gas bills.
